metadata.title: Daily Basic Polyester Low Cut Socks Ankle, No Show Men and Women Socks - 12
features: Premium Material & Finish: Made with lightweight polyester for softness, featuring built-in arch support and a touch of Spandex for a snug, ideal fit. These socks feature durable plain soles that reduce the appearance of stains, and are perfect for all types of footwear.

Each pack contains 12 pairs of soft low cut socks, perfect for a numerous situations such as: athletic, casual and business conditions including dancing, doing gym,running,shopping,working or travelling, and other indoor & outdoor activities.
Comfort & freshness your feet will love! These trendy socks are carefully designed to stay soft and breathable on your feet during your everyday activities.
Perfect Match: Three sizes are available (6-8, 9-11, 10-13) with simplest style fit for men and women featuring a good elasticity that can match any shoes style.
Available in Solid Black and White.No need to buy a different pair of socks for every pair of shoes, Daily Basic Wear offers the perfect no show socks that you can wear daily with all of your shoes!
description: Daily Basic Wear – It’s what we do best! The number one rule when wearing socks is don’t let them show! No need to buy a different pair of socks for every pair of shoes, Daily Basic Wear offers the perfect no show socks that you can wear daily with all of your shoes! Available is solid black and white, we present the pair of socks women, men, girls and boys love to wear for every event from working out to a night out. These socks are designed to bring you maximum comfort and top quality. They feature a reinforced heel and toe for enhanced durability and are made with a touch of stretch for ultimate comfort.
